                    <p class="otherText">A silly turn-based game about fighting skeletons.</p>
                    <a href="http://www.alexdomzalski.com/skeletonGauntlet/index.html">The Skeleton Gauntlet</a>
                    <p class="otherText">A silly turn-based game about fighting skeletons.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html> 